# Swift / SwiftUI Rules

Use pragmatic SwiftUI architecture.

## Preferred Structure

Default flow:

```text
Views
→ ViewModels
→ Services
→ Models
→ Persistence
```

## Guidelines

- Keep views small.
- Keep business logic out of views.
- Use view models for screen state and coordination.
- Use services for reusable operational logic.
- Prefer Apple frameworks.
- Avoid unnecessary dependencies.

## Testing

Prioritize tests for:

- Parsing
- Persistence
- Data transformation
- Business rules
- Regression fixes

## Documentation

Document why a type or function exists when it is not obvious.

Do not add noisy comments that merely repeat the code.
